query:
INSERT INTO blocks (
                height,
                hash,
                slot_time,
                block_time,
                baker_id,
                total_amount,
                total_staked,
                cumulative_num_txs
            ) VALUES (
                $1,
                $2,
                $3,
                (SELECT EXTRACT(MILLISECONDS FROM $3 - b.slot_time) FROM blocks b WHERE b.height = ($1 - 1::bigint)),
                $4,
                $5,
                $6,
                $7
            );
